Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats finally entered the New World, the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After landing on Punk Hazard; an island with two parts, one burning, the other frozen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,they learned about the hideous experiments performed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and headed off to investigate but as things got going,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.89,0:03:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they came to form an alliance with the Heart Pirates led by Trafalgar Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And Luffy finally encountered Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.95,0:03:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.50,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Law.
