Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.90,0:04:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think that he had no idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't trust Caesar, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.80,0:05:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he was being careful and sent an undercover agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Monet is that agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a Warlord-sama now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Vergo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just arrived. Luckily, I was at Dress Rosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a ride in an SAD tanker that was about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The right move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I cause any harm to you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.71,0:05:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,No but if you did, you'd be dead by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't fool grown-ups, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I should just finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.24,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to say it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vergo-san to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:37.05,"Sign",,0,0,0,,IN FRONT OF THE LABORATORY TEAM LUFFY
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.83,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tashigi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Vice Admiral Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I saw him get taken down twice a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of the Straw Hats got beaten, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it Conqueror's Haki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! There can't be that much difference in their strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what was it?! He beat all of them without even touching them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.91,0:07:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That serves you right, Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what our savior - Master is capable of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master! Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! Master! Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My strong soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tie these five up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Use Sea Prism Stone chains for the Devil Fruit users!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the Navy soldiers here and get inside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Something strange is raining down but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect this place where you belong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like the Cool Brothers blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Fighting against Straw Hat and Law must've been too much for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:37.17,"Sign",,0,0,0,,CENTER LAKE - TEAM ZORO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Brook. Convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of negotiation skill is going to work for these monsters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're merging into one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, they're merging into one another and getting bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.17,0:09:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It got bigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have a choice? It's my personal mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.48,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sanji, I'm a man! I've got to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.96,0:09:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about the Slimes behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the ass! That worthless chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... Don't... Don't attack me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's big, it's big!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you better not do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, don't! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.39,0:10:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you could do it, Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gas! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.96,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It's poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes, my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't have eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You jelly-ish body entity!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison gas, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do, Zoro-san?! It's poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the same thing before!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn from observation, skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were just unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.19,0:11:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the samurai's torso?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Let's use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Observation Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nowhere to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, they're jellies!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you eat and digest them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you stop talking to me like a bully?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm like 70 years older than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.57,0:12:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you call "grandpa"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still a lively skeleton...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Samurai-san?! T-T-Take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.50,0:12:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be the Slime's toxin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.91,0:12:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa-whoa, I hope his torso is not engulfed by it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been using Observation Haki for quite a while
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe the torso's getting weaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't distinguish its life force from that of the fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the matter?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you shithead! Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop chewing on it, shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I-It doesn't hurt at all! It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he bluffing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurts... Not really!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.74,0:13:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened to Sanji-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.53,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool, let it go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.09,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Joue Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I got the last piece safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The samurai puzzle will be complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison got this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! It's all around me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.39,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I do it with Nami-san's strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna put a strain on her body again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.50,0:14:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole lake is turning to the color of the poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't close up! Don't close up! Don't close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't close up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.06,0:15:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never felt so happy to just have my own body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.93,0:15:54.60,"Sign",,0,0,0,,THE SAMURAI FROM THE WANO KINGDOM FOXFIRE KIN'EMON
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I didn't know you were so tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as tall as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes! Excuse me for not introducing myself sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was born in Kuri, Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it already! I'm gonna freeze to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Poof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The coat will disappear once he takes it off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Funny-eyebrow man, what is your honorable name, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut the "sir" crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.42,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you have your whole body back so you've changed your attitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.08,0:16:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were insulting me so much earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,hiding behind the fact you were disabled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you're not forgetting what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder you people are barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like pirates! You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't irritate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just ask me to find your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna owe anything to pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't ask you even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm not even capable of fighting back if someone hits me
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can carry me if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.25,0:17:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I will never forget your kindness for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And please forgive me for having doubts about you all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...until I got my torso back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you! I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, fool! Lift your head up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Men shouldn't kneel on the ground that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you, sir, weren't there, I probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm sorry to interrupt you but, Sanji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.67,0:18:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look. You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:35.20,"Sign",,0,0,0,,THE THIRD LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could find out how he made the drug...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.40,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! It's a book about drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.38,0:19:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I gotta look for sedatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, the airship is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.47,0:19:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:20:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about time for them to have these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Put Straw Hat and the others in a cage and carry it to my chambers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have nowhere to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.22,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Didn't I tell you to do something about them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.91,0:20:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped because we couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be such children, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.80,0:20:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't cause any damage to Nami-san's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.91,0:20:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This body...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.52,0:20:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This body, I have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna return it, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we burn them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.80,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.36,0:20:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,People call me Foxfire Kin'emon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can burn and slice an enemy with my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me burn them down and clear the way to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can burn and slice an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:22:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He cut the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I cleared the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming for you, Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! I'm still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we were engulfed by the fire from the explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,K-K-Kin'emon-san? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just cut the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.47,0:22:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The explosion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My Foxfire Style
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,allows me to cut something with fire and then cut flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.08,0:22:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no flame that I can't cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm going to go to the laboratory to save Momonosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.62,0:22:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm intrigued by a samurai's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you to rescue your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.84,0:23:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious individual appears and manages\Nto injure Law with overwhelming strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.67,0:23:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While the horrifying truth of this individual\Nleaves the Straw Hats shocked,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,it's nothing compared to\Nwhen they discover the true identity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of the mastermind behind Caesar and the enigmatic man!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.11,0:23:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shocking!\NThe Mystery Man's True Identity—Vergo!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
